profile_positions.description:
Main responsibilities within the occupied position:
- we have established and maintained the contractual relations with the company's clients, in accordance with the observance of the price policy of the company in force;
- I supervised and coordinated the waste collection activity for the designated area;
- I coordinated a team of 4 colleagues to accomplish the tasks set in accordance with the company's objectives;
- I followed the elaboration and observance of the established legal circuit of the documents provided by the waste collection legislation;
- I have temporarily taken over a number of delegates of the Executive Director within the adjacent area;
- I have elaborated and presented to the company management the monthly sales plan, as well as the activity report;
- we have been developing the commercial policy of the company by increasing the number of clients in the allocated area;

- Analyzing requests coming from HP partners from Middle East and
Kingdom of Saudi Arabia and offering them support on the E2E process;
- Managing all quality policies, procedures, processes, programs, and
practices, to ensure continuous compliance with appropriate standards and
guidelines;
- Finding solutions for standardizing the process and first point of contact for
partner and sales queries;
- Delivering offers in a pre-settled turnaround time and identifying the reasons
causing delays;
- Offering pricing analysis for products further sold to end customers;
- Mentoring non-experienced team members on day-to-day activities.

Support sales team:
• Participation in the implementation of price offers;
• Provide excellent collaboration between teams and departments involved;
• Ensure a good collaboration with the team at special prices EMEA and
country managers in Bucharest;
• Ensuring documenting, reporting and optimizing operational processes.
• Ensuring the accuracy of the information contained in quantity.
• Validating and ensuring the correctness of the information received
regarding the price offers.

Being part of contracts team I have facilitated the development of various
separation processes along HP EMEA such as:
• responsibility to inform partners about separation HP EMEA and providing
specific documentation;
• performing improve data quality for better alignment with sales processes;
• solving tasks ad - hoc analysis requested by the deadlines agreed (examples:
changes of partners, contacts, updating large amounts of data, creating a new
set of contracts and amendments for different regions), etc;
• participation in all team meetings, department meetings;
• I have worked with the team of Support Tools;

- Check the status of stocks , making transfers and adjustments of stocks ;
- Solving punctual situations that may occur during physical distribution process ;
- A good interaction with logistics service providers ;
- Accomplishments reports and statements in MS Excel and SAP ;
- Distribution of billing services to its customers ;
